// Schema-rooted §J follow-up (nested generics): two-hop generic
// substitution through a cross-module value path.
// `pkg.w.inner.value` must thread `T → Int` from `Wrapper<Int>`
// into the field `Container<T> inner`, then into `T value` on the
// inner schema. Declared `#main() -> Int` lands cleanly when both
// substitutions plus the namespace re-qualification fire.
#import pkg from "./lib_with_nested_generic_value.relon"
#main() -> Int
pkg.w.inner.value
